#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.join.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.join"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.join:1 of
msgid "Join columns of another DataFrame."
msgstr "连接另一个 DataFrame 的列。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.join:3 of
msgid ""
"Join columns with `other` DataFrame either on index or on a key column. "
"Efficiently join multiple DataFrame objects by index at once by passing a"
" list."
msgstr ""
"将列与 `other` DataFrame 按索引或键列连接。通过传递一个列表，可以高效地"
"一次性按索引连接多个 DataFrame 对象。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.join of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.join:7 of
msgid ""
"Index should be similar to one of the columns in this one. If a Series is"
" passed, its name attribute must be set, and that will be used as the "
"column name in the resulting joined DataFrame."
msgstr ""
"索引应与此 DataFrame 中的某一列相似。如果传递的是 Series，则必须设置其 "
"name 属性，该属性将用作结果连接 DataFrame 中的列名。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.join:11 of
msgid ""
"Column or index level name(s) in the caller to join on the index in "
"`other`, otherwise joins index-on-index. If multiple values given, the "
"`other` DataFrame must have a MultiIndex. Can pass an array as the join "
"key if it is not already contained in the calling DataFrame. Like an "
"Excel VLOOKUP operation."
msgstr ""
"调用方中用于与 `other` 中索引连接的列或索引层级名称，否则按索引与索引连接"
"。如果给定多个值，`other` DataFrame 必须具有 MultiIndex。如果连接键不在"
"调用方 DataFrame 中，可以传递一个数组。类似 Excel 的 VLOOKUP 操作。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.join:17 of
msgid ""
"How to handle the operation of the two objects.  * left: use calling "
"frame's index (or column if on is specified) * right: use `other`'s "
"index. * outer: form union of calling frame's index (or column if on is"
"   specified) with `other`'s index, and sort it.   lexicographically. * "
"inner: form intersection of calling frame's index (or column if   on is "
"specified) with `other`'s index, preserving the order   of the calling's "
"one."
msgstr ""
"如何处理两个对象的操作。  * left：使用调用方的索引（如果指定了 on，则使用"
"列） * right：使用 `other` 的索引。 * outer：将调用方的索引（如果指定了 "
"on，则使用列）与 `other` 的索引取并集，并按字典序排序。 * inner：将调用方"
"的索引（如果指定了 on，则使用列）与 `other` 的索引取交集，并保留调用方的"
"顺序。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.join:17 of
msgid "How to handle the operation of the two objects."
msgstr "如何处理两个对象的操作。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.join:19 of
msgid "left: use calling frame's index (or column if on is specified)"
msgstr "left: 使用调用框架的索引（或如果指定了 on 则使用列）"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.join:20 of
msgid "right: use `other`'s index."
msgstr "right: 使用 `other` 的索引。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.join:21 of
msgid ""
"outer: form union of calling frame's index (or column if on is specified)"
" with `other`'s index, and sort it. lexicographically."
msgstr ""
"outer: 形成调用框架的索引（或如果指定了 on 则使用列）与 `other` 索引的并"
"集，并按字典序排序。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.join:24 of
msgid ""
"inner: form intersection of calling frame's index (or column if on is "
"specified) with `other`'s index, preserving the order of the calling's "
"one."
msgstr ""
"inner: 形成调用框架的索引（或如果指定了 on 则使用列）与 `other` 索引的"
"交集，保持调用框架的顺序。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.join:28 of
msgid "Suffix to use from left frame's overlapping columns."
msgstr "来自左框中重叠列的后缀。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.join:30 of
msgid "Suffix to use from right frame's overlapping columns."
msgstr "来自右框中重叠列的后缀。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.join:32 of
msgid ""
"Order result DataFrame lexicographically by the join key. If False, the "
"order of the join key depends on the join type (how keyword)."
msgstr ""
"按连接键对结果 DataFrame 进行字典序排序。如果为 False，则连接键的顺序"
"取决于连接类型（how 关键字）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.join:35 of
msgid ""
"\"broadcast\" is recommended when one DataFrame is much smaller than the "
"other, otherwise, \"shuffle\" will be a better choice. By default, we "
"choose method according to actual data size."
msgstr ""
"当一个 DataFrame 远小于另一个时，建议使用 \"broadcast\"，否则 \"shuffle\""
" 是更好的选择。默认情况下，我们会根据实际数据大小选择方法。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.join:39 of
msgid ""
"Auto merge small chunks before or after merge  * \"both\": auto merge "
"small chunks before and after, * \"none\": do not merge small chunks * "
"\"before\": only merge small chunks before merge * \"after\": only merge "
"small chunks after merge"
msgstr ""
"在合并前后自动合并小块  * \"both\"：在合并前后都自动合并小块， * \"none\""
"：不合并小块 * \"before\"：仅在合并前合并小块 * \"after\"：仅在合并后合并"
"小块"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.join:39 of
msgid "Auto merge small chunks before or after merge"
msgstr "在合并之前或之后自动合并小块"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.join:41 of
msgid "\"both\": auto merge small chunks before and after,"
msgstr "\"both\": 在合并之前和之后自动合并小块，"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.join:42 of
msgid "\"none\": do not merge small chunks"
msgstr "\"none\": 不合并小块"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.join:43 of
msgid "\"before\": only merge small chunks before merge"
msgstr "\"before\": 仅在合并之前合并小块"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.join:44 of
msgid "\"after\": only merge small chunks after merge"
msgstr "\"after\": 仅在合并之后合并小块"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.join:46 of
msgid ""
"When how is \"inner\", merged result could be much smaller than original "
"DataFrame, if the number of chunks is greater than the threshold, it will"
" merge small chunks automatically."
msgstr ""
"当 how 为 \"inner\" 时，合并结果可能远小于原始 DataFrame，如果块数超过"
"阈值，将自动合并小块。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.join:50 of
msgid "Use bloom filter to optimize merge"
msgstr "使用布隆过滤器优化合并"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.join:52 of
msgid ""
"* \"max_elements\": max elements in bloom filter,   default value is the "
"max size of all input chunks * \"error_rate\": error raite, default 0.1. "
"* \"apply_chunk_size_threshold\": min chunk size of input chunks to apply"
" bloom filter, default 10   when chunk size of left and right is greater "
"than this threshold, apply bloom filter * \"filter\": \"large\", "
"\"small\", \"both\", default \"large\"   decides to filter on large, "
"small or both DataFrames."
msgstr ""
"* \"max_elements\"：布隆过滤器中的最大元素数，默认值为所有输入块的最大"
"大小 * \"error_rate\"：错误率，默认为 0.1 * \"apply_chunk_size_threshold"
"\"：应用布隆过滤器的最小输入块大小，默认为 10 当左右块大小超过此阈值时，"
"应用布隆过滤器 * \"filter\"：\"large\", \"small\", \"both\"，默认为 \""
"large\" 决定在大、小或两个 DataFrame 上进行过滤。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.join:53 of
msgid ""
"\"max_elements\": max elements in bloom filter, default value is the max "
"size of all input chunks"
msgstr "\"max_elements\"：布隆过滤器中的最大元素数，默认值为所有输入块的最大大小"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.join:55 of
msgid "\"error_rate\": error raite, default 0.1."
msgstr "\"error_rate\"：错误率，默认为 0.1。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.join:56 of
msgid ""
"\"apply_chunk_size_threshold\": min chunk size of input chunks to apply "
"bloom filter, default 10 when chunk size of left and right is greater "
"than this threshold, apply bloom filter"
msgstr ""
"\"apply_chunk_size_threshold\"：应用布隆过滤器的最小输入块大小，默认为 10"
" 当左右块大小超过此阈值时，应用布隆过滤器"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.join:58 of
msgid ""
"\"filter\": \"large\", \"small\", \"both\", default \"large\" decides to "
"filter on large, small or both DataFrames."
msgstr ""
"\"filter\"：\"large\", \"small\", \"both\"，默认为 \"large\" 决定在大、小"
"或两个 DataFrame 上进行过滤。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.join:61 of
msgid ""
"Join strategy to use for left frame. When data skew occurs, consider "
"these strategies to avoid long-tail issues, but use them cautiously to "
"prevent OOM and unnecessary overhead."
msgstr ""
"左侧 DataFrame 使用的连接策略。当出现数据倾斜时，可以考虑使用这些策略来"
"避免长尾问题，但应谨慎使用以防止内存溢出和不必要的开销。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.join:64 of
msgid "Join strategy to use for right frame."
msgstr "右侧 DataFrame 使用的连接策略。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.join of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.join:67 of
msgid "A dataframe containing columns from both the caller and `other`."
msgstr "一个包含调用者和 `other` 列的 DataFrame。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.join of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.join:72 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.merge`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.join:73 of
msgid "For column(s)-on-column(s) operations."
msgstr "用于列与列之间的操作。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.join:76 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.join:99 of
msgid "Join DataFrames using their indexes."
msgstr "使用索引连接 DataFrame。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.join:110 of
msgid ""
"If we want to join using the key columns, we need to set key to be the "
"index in both `df` and `other`. The joined DataFrame will have key as its"
" index."
msgstr ""
"如果我们想使用关键列进行连接，则需要将 `df` 和 `other` 中的关键列设为索引"
"。连接后的 DataFrame 将以该关键列为索引。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.join:124 of
msgid ""
"Another option to join using the key columns is to use the `on` "
"parameter. DataFrame.join always uses `other`'s index but we can use any "
"column in `df`. This method preserves the original DataFrame's index in "
"the result."
msgstr ""
"另一种使用关键列进行连接的方法是使用 `on` 参数。DataFrame.join 总是使用 `"
"other` 的索引，但我们可以使用 `df` 中的任意列。此方法会在结果中保留原始 "
"DataFrame 的索引。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.merge.merge.join:138 of
msgid "Using non-unique key values shows how they are matched."
msgstr "使用非唯一键值可以展示它们是如何匹配的。"

